1139
01:47:16,351 --> 01:47:17,751
If you call the cops,

1140
01:47:19,112 --> 01:47:20,352
I'll leave, too.

1141
01:47:20,992 --> 01:47:21,992
Are you stupid?

1142
01:47:22,472 --> 01:47:23,352
Yes.

1143
01:48:21,00 --> 01:48:22,401
Where are you going?

1144
01:48:23,441 --> 01:48:24,521
I don't understand.

1145
01:48:25,361 --> 01:48:28,561
I trust Carlos, and I believe him.
I want to know more.

1146
01:48:28,721 --> 01:48:30,402
That's the easy part.

1147
01:48:30,922 --> 01:48:32,562
Believing what you want.

1148
01:48:32,842 --> 01:48:34,082
What pleases you.

1149
01:48:34,282 --> 01:48:36,323
I did that, too.
Until tonight.

1150
01:48:36,523 --> 01:48:38,283
I'll chase whomever I please!

1151
01:48:39,083 --> 01:48:41,443
Men matter less and less to me.

1152
01:48:41,683 --> 01:48:42,683
That's my lot.

1153
01:48:43,364 --> 01:48:44,964
They've never given me anything.

1154
01:48:45,364 --> 01:48:46,404
Except sex.

1155
01:48:46,644 --> 01:48:49,284
No? What about the keeper?

1156
01:48:50,765 --> 01:48:52,325
What? Besides wild sex

1157
01:48:52,525 --> 01:48:53,565
and a daughter?

1158
01:48:55,165 --> 01:48:56,565
Don't forget that story

1159
01:48:56,765 --> 01:48:59,526
full of advantages that
he wrote just for you!

1160
01:49:00,086 --> 01:49:01,286
That's right.

1161
01:49:02,06 --> 01:49:04,06
Maybe your boyfriend
was the last

1162
01:49:04,207 --> 01:49:05,967
- good man on earth.
- No, he wasn't.

1163
01:49:07,327 --> 01:49:10,447
You're wrong,
but that's my business.

1164
01:49:10,927 --> 01:49:13,768
And I suppose Carlos
is also your business.

1165
01:49:14,168 --> 01:49:15,368
Yours alone.

1166
01:49:15,888 --> 01:49:17,848
You're the only one chasing him.

1167
01:49:19,289 --> 01:49:20,169
Yeah.

1168
01:49:21,049 --> 01:49:22,529
Come to think of it,

1169
01:49:22,729 --> 01:49:25,290
I always chase men.
When I like them.

1170
01:49:25,810 --> 01:49:27,410
To each his own, right?

1171
01:49:31,730 --> 01:49:33,211
Where could he be?

1172
01:49:34,451 --> 01:49:37,011
I don't know. I'm going home.

1173
01:49:37,211 --> 01:49:38,931
You guys cook tonight.

1174
01:52:47,998 --> 01:52:49,559
I'm so sorry.

1175
01:54:05,370 --> 01:54:07,010
Carlos! It's me, Lucía.

1176
01:54:07,210 --> 01:54:09,170
I want to come down.

1177
01:54:10,730 --> 01:54:12,131
Come and help me.

1178
01:54:13,091 --> 01:54:15,651
I know how to dive, too.
What did you think?

1179
01:54:21,412 --> 01:54:23,372
Lucía. It's me, Elena.

1180
01:54:34,574 --> 01:54:35,654
Where's Carlos?

1181
01:54:36,054 --> 01:54:37,334
Down there.

1182
01:54:37,654 --> 01:54:38,934
Did he escape?

1183
01:54:41,095 --> 01:54:42,135
Maybe he's dead.

1184
01:54:46,375 --> 01:54:49,776
If he turns up,
we have to believe him, okay?

1185
01:54:50,816 --> 01:54:52,136
Whatever you want.

1186
01:54:52,776 --> 01:54:53,856
That's right.

1187
01:54:55,057 --> 01:54:56,257
He's a crab.

1188
01:54:59,697 --> 01:55:00,777
Let's go home.

1189
01:55:01,017 --> 01:55:01,978
What for?

1190
01:55:02,218 --> 01:55:03,218
To eat.

1191
01:55:03,458 --> 01:55:04,218
So early?

1192
01:55:05,858 --> 01:55:06,898
I'm not hungry.

1193
01:55:07,298 --> 01:55:09,899
Tough. It's about time
you helped me cook.

1194
01:55:11,499 --> 01:55:14,779
We'll make a special meal
and we'll be together

1195
01:55:15,620 --> 01:55:16,860
and have fun.

1196
01:55:33,382 --> 01:55:35,422
You're a gift to this earth.

1197
01:55:36,663 --> 01:55:39,743
Elena. You're crying.

1198
01:55:43,103 --> 01:55:46,224
Tears of happiness,
which is what I am from now on.

1199
01:55:46,424 --> 01:55:48,384
Great. I hope it's contagious.

1200
01:55:48,584 --> 01:55:50,185
Piece of cake.
Let's go.

1201
01:58:51,610 --> 01:58:54,971
