1204
01:59:02,372 --> 01:59:04,612
And the story
starts again halfway.

1205
01:59:06,132 --> 01:59:09,013
The other advantage,
and the biggest,

1206
01:59:09,653 --> 01:59:12,733
is that you can change course
along the way...

1207
01:59:12,893 --> 01:59:15,814
If you let me.
If you give me time.

1208
01:59:58,660 --> 01:59:59,860
A ray of sunshine...

